data.text:
Samvel Karapetian was an Armenian historian, researcher, author, and expert of medieval architecture, specializing in the study of the historical monuments of Armenia, Nagorno Karabakh and other regions of the Southern Caucasus.

Samvel Karapetyan was born on July 30, 1961, in Yerevan, Yerevan, Armenia. His birth geographical coordinates are 40° 10’ 52” North latitude and 44° 30’ 49” East longitude. Samvel Karapetyan passed away at the age of 58 in 2020.

Astrologically, Samvel Karapetyan falls under the Sun sign of Leo, with Libra as his Ascendant, Pisces as his Moon sign, and Leo as his Black Moon Lilith sign.
